'''BWI机场站'''是[[美国|美国]][[马里兰州|马里兰州]]{{link-en|林西克姆 (马里兰州)|Linthicum, Maryland|林西克姆}}[[巴尔的摩/华盛顿瑟古德·马歇尔国际机场|巴尔的摩机场]]附近的多式联运车站，本站有[[东北走廊|东北走廊]]经过，部分美铁列车和[[馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路|馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路]]（MARC）[[宾州线|宾州线]]列车在本站停靠。本站是美国第一个空铁联运车站，距离巴尔的摩机场航站楼约1英里<ref>{{cite web|url=http://history.amtrak.com/archives/bwi-rail-station-dedication-booklet-1980|title=BWI Rail Station dedication booklet, 1980.|publisher=[[Amtrak|Amtrak]]|access-date=September 30, 2013|archive-date=2020-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302063434/https://history.amtrak.com/archives/bwi-rail-station-dedication-booklet-1980/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有免费接驳巴士联通<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bwiairport.com/en/travel/ground-transportation/trans/amtrak |title=Ground Transportation: Amtrak |publisher=[[Maryland_Aviation_Administration|Maryland Aviation Administration]] |access-date=May 9, 2017 |archive-date=2017-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724172909/http://www.bwiairport.com/en/travel/ground-transportation/trans/amtrak |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

本站是美铁中大西洋地区第六繁忙的车站，次于[[紐約賓夕法尼亞車站|紐約賓夕法尼亞車站]]、[[華盛頓聯合車站|華盛頓聯合車站]]、[[30街車站|费城30街車站]]、[[巴爾的摩賓夕法尼亞車站|巴爾的摩賓夕法尼亞車站]]、{{link-en|奥尔巴尼-伦斯勒车站|Albany–Rensselaer station}}，巴尔的摩-华盛顿走廊间第三繁忙的车站。

==历史==
[[File:Bill_Norman_speaking_at_BWI_Rail_Station_dedication,_October_1980.jpg|thumb]]

车站的构想最初由一名叫查尔斯·阿德勒的巴尔的摩交通发明家于1964年提出<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rasmussen |first1=Charles |title=In Traffic, He Saw the Light |url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1999-09-11/features/9909110352_1_charles-adler-signal-actuated |access-date=2018-06-11 |newspaper=The Baltimore Sun |date=1999-09-11 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162133/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1999-09-11/features/9909110352_1_charles-adler-signal-actuated |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并于1980年10月23日开通。巧合的是，车站开通时阿德勒刚好去世不久。美铁和[[聯合鐵路|聯合鐵路]]（现MARC）的列车服务于3天后开始<ref>Air-Rail Station To Open ''[[Amtrak_News|Amtrak News]]'' September 1, 1980 page 3</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=BWI Airport Rail Link Celebrates Opening |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=October 24, 1980 |first=Carole |last=Shifrin |page=D3 |id = {{ProQuest|147198286}}}}</ref>。

车站站房设有售票柜台、候车室和商业店铺。1990年代车站新建设有3200车位的停车楼一座，取代了原先位于地面的地车场。停车楼为利用车站前往华盛顿或巴尔的摩的通勤人士提供停车位，同时还设有巴士总站。目前停车楼仍存在不敷应用的问题<ref>{{cite web|title=Availability of MARC Parking|url=http://www.mtamaryland.com/services/marc/serviceInformation/Parking_Camden_Penn.cfm|access-date=July 13, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080712223114/http://www.mtamaryland.com/services/marc/serviceInformation/Parking_Camden_Penn.cfm|archive-date=July 12, 2008}}</ref>。

{{link-en|卡罗莱纳人号列车|Carolinian (train)}}曾于1991年至2004年停靠本站。

2006年至2010年，车站曾对{{convert|1050|ft|m}}长的高站台进行翻新及延长工程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.progressiverailroading.com/news/article/Maryland-Transit-Administration-renovates-BWI-station-platforms--25130|title=Maryland Transit Administration renovates BWI station platforms|work=Progressive Railroading|publisher=Trade Press Media Group, Inc.|date=November 24, 2010|access-date=September 30, 2013|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303060956/https://www.progressiverailroading.com/news/article/Maryland-Transit-Administration-renovates-BWI-station-platforms--25130|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新站台采用拼装混凝土，设有指示牌、照明、候车室、风雨棚等设施<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mta.maryland.gov/services/marc/serviceInformation/MARC_Council_January_2010_Meeting_MInutes.pdf |title=MARC Council January 2010 Meeting Minutes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100223223839/http://mta.maryland.gov/services/marc/serviceInformation/MARC_Council_January_2010_Meeting_MInutes.pdf |archive-date=February 23, 2010 }}</ref>。

===扩建===
[[File:BWI_Rail_Station_construction,_June_2019.jpeg|thumb]]

2010年，当地为车站集资940万美元，用作新站房及第四轨工程设计的经费，而建设资金预计将耗费8000万至一亿美元<ref>{{cite press release |title=Governor O'Malley Applauds President Obama for High Speed Rail Investment in Maryland |url=http://www.governor.maryland.gov/pressreleases/100128.asp |publisher=[[Maryland|State of Maryland]] |date=January 28, 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203232940/http://www.governor.maryland.gov/pressreleases/100128.asp |archive-date=February 3, 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Maryland has plans for bigger BWI rail station |url=http://www.rtands.com/newsflash/maryland-has-plans-for-bigger-bwi-rail-station.html |magazine=Railway Track and Structures |publisher=Simmons-Boardman Publishing |location=New York |date=September 9, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715210545/http://www.rtands.com/newsflash/maryland-has-plans-for-bigger-bwi-rail-station.html |archive-date=July 15, 2011 }}</ref>。{{link-en|马里兰州交通部|Maryland Department of Transportation}}为此于2011年申请了3亿美元的联邦资助，但未获批准<ref name=moves>{{cite news |url=https://www.capitalgazette.com/news/environment/ph-ac-cn-bwi-rail-0205-20160205-story.html |title=BWI Rail Station expansion moves forward |newspaper=Capital Gazette |date=February 5, 2016 |first=Shanteé |last=Woodards |accessdate=2021-02-20 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214094802/https://www.capitalgazette.com/news/environment/ph-ac-cn-bwi-rail-0205-20160205-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[聯邦鐵路管理局|聯邦鐵路管理局]]于2016年2月发布了结果为“无显著环境影响”{{link-en|国家环境政策法|National Environmental Policy Act|环境评估}}，为集资问题解决后的施工扫清了道路<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.fra.dot.gov/eLib/Details/L17334 |title=FRA Gives Green Light to Rebuild BWI Rail Station, Increase Service and Reliability |publisher=Federal Railroad Administration |date=February 4, 2016 |access-date=February 4, 2016 |archive-date=2017-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511075006/https://www.fra.dot.gov/eLib/Details/L17334 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。项目还包括一条长{{convert|9.4|miles}}的第四轨，预计耗资6亿美元<ref name=moves />。

2018年8月27日，马里兰州交通部开始了耗资470万美元的新站房建设工程，在新站房建设期间老站房仍将继续使用<ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.mta.maryland.gov/articles/207 |publisher=Maryland Department of Transportation Maryland Transit Administration |title=MDOT MTA Begins $4.7 Million Renovation of BWI Airport Rail Station on August 27 |date=August 22, 2018 |access-date=2021-02-20 |archive-date=2021-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424055244/https://www.mta.maryland.gov/articles/207 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新站房于2019年10月启用，剪彩仪式则于12月进行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://csanders429.wordpress.com/2019/10/13/bwi-station-reopens-with-new-facilities/ |title=BWI Station Reopens With New Facilities |work=Amtrak in the Heartland |date=October 13, 2019 |first=Craig |last=Sanders |access-date=2021-02-20 |archive-date=2019-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191221032115/https://csanders429.wordpress.com/2019/10/13/bwi-station-reopens-with-new-facilities/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=overpass />。

然而改建工程并没有涉及存在漏水问题、由美铁拥有的天桥，亦没有在车站提供WiFi服务。MTA回应称其所有管辖的车站不会提供WiFi服务，但其正与美铁协商天桥维修事宜<ref name=overpass>{{cite news |url=https://www.baltimoresun.com/politics/bs-md-pol-bwi-marc-station-20191210-swp7olfiyzd6lgvhokv63vzee4-story.html |title=$4.7 million renovation of BWI Rail Station adds passenger amenities but doesn’t fix leaky walkway roof |newspaper=Baltimore Sun |date=December 10, 2019 |first=Colin |last=Campbell |accessdate=2021-02-20 |archive-date=2021-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304195223/https://www.baltimoresun.com/politics/bs-md-pol-bwi-marc-station-20191210-swp7olfiyzd6lgvhokv63vzee4-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==车站结构==
[[File:2017_BWI_Rail_Station_01.jpg|thumb]]
BWI机场站是美铁[[东北走廊|东北走廊]]上的中间站，有部分[[阿西乐特快|阿西乐特快]]、[[东北区域号|东北区域号]]、{{link-en|佛蒙特人号列车|Vermonter (train)|佛蒙特人号}}和{{link-en|帕尔梅托号列车|Palmetto (train)}}停靠。车站也是[[馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路|馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路]]（MARC）[[宾州线|宾州线]]的停靠车站。

本站不设有行李托运服务，因此本站是美铁系统内最繁忙的无托运服务车站。

